20case%20was%20lodged%20at%2012.10%20am%20in%20Gwalior%20for%20the%20theft%20of%20a%20motorcycle%20worth%20Rs%201.80%20lakh%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Delhi%2C%20the%20first%20case%20was%20filed%20against%20a%20street%20vendor%20for%20obstructing%20a%20road%20near%20the%20station.%20The%20FIR%20was%20filed%20under%20Section%20285%20of%20the%20new%20criminal%20code%20that%20states%2C%20%26quot%3BWhoever%2C%20by%20doing%20any%20act%2C%20or%20by%20omitting%20to%20take%20order%20with%20any%20property%20in%20his%20possession%20or%20under%20his%20charge%2C%20causes%20danger%2C%20obstruction%20or%20injury%20to%20any%20person%20in%20any%20public%20way%20or%20public%20line%20of%20navigation%2C%20shall%20be%20punished%20with%20fine%20which%20may%20extend%20to%20five%20thousand%20rupees.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20FIR%20was%20filed%20after%20a%20police%20personnel%20on%20patrol%20duty%20last%20night%20spotted%20the%20street%20vendor%20selling%20water%20bottles%20and%20gutkha%20on%20the%20road.%20His%20makeshift%20stall%20had%20obstructed%20the%20road%20and%20he%20was%20repeatedly%20asked%20to%20move%20it.%20When%20he%20did%20not%2C%20the%20police%20personnel%20moved%20to%20register%20an%20FIR.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20copy%20of%20the%20FIR%2C%20which%20is%20with%20NDTV%2C%20states%20that%20the%20street%20vendor%20had%20parked%20his%20stall%20near%20under%20a%20foot%20over%20bridge%20near%20New%20Delhi%20Railway%20Station%20late%20last%20night.%20%26quot%3BThe%20man%20was%20selling%20water%2C%20bidi%20and%20cigarettes%20on%20the%20street%20and%20the%20obstruction%20was%20causing%20difficulty%20for%20the%20public.%20The%20sub-inspector%20asked%20the%20man%20several%20times%20to%20remove%20the%20stall%20from%20the%20road%2C%20but%20he%20did%20not%20comply.%20The%20sub-inspector%20asked%20several%20passers-by%20to%20join%20the%20probe%2C%20but%20they%20refused.%20Then%20the%20sub-inspector%20shot%20a%20video%20using%20the%20e-praman%20application%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20FIR%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20man%20has%20been%20identified%20as%20Pankaj%20Kumar%20from%20Patna%20in%20Bihar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThree%20new%20criminal%20codes%20--%20Bharatiya%20Nyaya%20Sanhita%2C%20Bharatiya%20Nagarik%20Suraksha%20Sanhita%20and%20the%20Bharatiya%20Sakshya%20Adhiniyam%20--%20have%20come%20into%20force%20today.%20They%20will%20replace%20the%20colonial-era%20Indian%20Penal%20Code%2C%20Indian%20Evidence%20Act%20and%20the%20Code%20of%20Criminal%20Procedure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20criminal%20codes%20have%20been%20changed%20with%20an%20objective%20of%20ensuring%20speedy%20justice%20and%20to%20tackle%20new%20kinds%20of%20crime.%20Judgments%20are%20now%20required%20within%2045%20days%20of%20completion%20of%20trial%20and%20charges%20must%20be%20framed%20within%2060%20days%20of%20first%20hearing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnion%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20has%20said%20the%20change%20was%20made%20to%20ensure%20%26quot%3Bspeedy%20justice%20and%20justice%20to%20all%26quot%3B.%20The%20Opposition%20parties%2C%20including%20the%20Congress%2C%20say%20the%20decision%20to%20implement%20the%20new%20criminal%20laws%20has%20been%20taken%20in%20haste.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719824280000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Folj5u4a8_police-generic-image_625x300_18_June_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnew-criminal-laws-1st-case-under-new-penal-code-filed-against-delhis-street-vendor-6006809%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22As%20the%20Bharatiya%20Nyay%20Sanhita%20came%20into%20force%20today%2C%20the%20first%20FIR%20was%20filed%20against%20a%20street%20vendor%20for%20obstructing%20a%20road%20near%20New%20Delhi%20Railway%20Station.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnew-criminal-laws-1st-case-under-new-penal-code-filed-against-delhis-street-vendor-6006809%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2F