0the%20film%20is%20being%20shot%20on%20a%20detailed%20set%20on%20the%20outskirts%20of%20Bangalore.%20Originally%20set%20to%20feature%20Kareena%20Kapoor%20Khan%2C%20the%20film%20now%20stars%20Nayanthara%2C%20with%20Shruti%20Haasan%20replacing%20Sai%20Pallavi%20as%20Yash's%20love%20interest.%20Scheduled%20for%20release%20on%20April%2010%2C%202025%2C%20the%20teaser%20has%20already%20captured%20attention%20with%20its%20promise%20of%20a%20compelling%20narrative.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fyash-to-bring-1950s-and-1970s-eras-to-toxic-a-fairy-tale-for-grown-ups%2Farticleshow%2F111400925.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BJustice%20Replaces%20Punishment%20In%20New%20Criminal%20Laws%26quot%3B%3A%20Amit%20Shah%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EJustice%20replaces%20punishment%20in%20the%20three%20new%20criminal%20laws%20that%20came%20into%20force%20today%2C%20Union%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20has%20said.%20Mr%20Shah%2C%20who%20led%20the%20exercise%20to%20review%20the%20country's%20criminal%20law%20system%2C%20told%20the%20media%20today%20that%2077%20years%20after%20Independence%2C%20the%20country%20has%20a%20completely%20'swadeshi'%20legal%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20overhaul%20of%20the%20colonial-era%20criminal%20code%2C%20an%20%26quot%3BIndian%20soul%26quot%3B%20has%20been%20added%20to%20the%20justice%20system%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20provisions%20are%20such%20they%20many%20groups%20would%20be%20benefited.%20Many%20sections%20from%20the%20British%20era%20have%20been%20replaced%20by%20sections%20in%20sync%20with%20today.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20crimes%20relating%20to%20violence%20against%20women%2C%20Mr%20Shah%20said%20the%20new%20law%20provides%20for%20recording%20the%20survivor's%20statement%20at%20her%20home%20and%20also%20mentioned%20an%20online%20FIR%20facility%20that%20will%20shield%20her%20from%20social%20stigma.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20was%20no%20provision%20in%20law%20for%20mob%20lynching%20case.%20It%20has%20now%20been%20defined.%20This%20was%20a%20longstanding%20demand.%20Also%2C%20we%20have%20completely%20removed%20the%20section%20of%20treason%20and%20brought%20a%20new%20section%20for%20anti-national%20activities.%20Earlier%2C%20it%20was%20a%20crime%20to%20make%20a%20statement%20against%20the%20government.%20Now%2C%20a%20law%20will%20provide%20for%20action%20against%20attempts%20to%20harm%20India's%20unity%20and%20sovereignty%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20sharing%20the%20highlights%20of%20the%20new%20criminal%20codes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Shah%20said%20the%20new%20criminal%20laws%20would%20create%20a%20modern%20legal%20system.%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20not%20just%20imbibed%20technology%2C%20but%20have%20pre-empted%20technological%20changes%20that%20may%20take%20place%20over%20the%20next%2050%20years.%20I%20believe%20this%20will%20be%20the%20world's%20most%20modern%20criminal%20justice%20system.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Shah%20said%20videography%20is%20now%20mandatory%20during%20search%20and%20seizure%20exercises%20so%20that%20no%20one%20can%20be%20framed.%20The%20e-statement%20of%20a%20survivor%20of%20rape%20or%20sexual%20harassment%20is%20legally%20valid%20now%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20laws%2C%20he%20said%2C%20are%20victim%20centric.%20%26quot%3BEarlier%2C%20police%20picked%20someone%20up%20and%20his%20family%20members%20had%20to%20go%20to%20court.%20Now%20we%20have%20made%20it%20compulsory%20to%20maintain%20a%20register%20and%20e-register%20at%20every%20police%20station%20that%20will%20list%20which%20criminal%20is%20in%20police%20custody.%20So%20a%20habeus%20corpus%20plea%20in%20court%20won't%20be%20needed%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20Searches%20and%20raids%2C%20he%20said%2C%20would%20be%20videographed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20sharing%20the%20highlights%20of%20the%20new%20criminal%20codes%2C%20Mr%20Shah%20proceeded%20to%20hit%20back%20at%20Opposition%20leaders'%20remarks%20on%20the%20laws.%20The%20main%20opposition%20has%20alleged%20that%20the%20news%20laws%20were%20not%20properly%20debated%20upon%20and%20that%20the%20legislation%20related%20to%20them%20was%20%26quot%3Bforcibly%26quot%3B%20passed%20in%20Parliament%20after%20146%20Opposition%20MPs%20were%20suspended.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20response%2C%20Mr%20Shah%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20Lok%20Sabha%20debated%20this%20for%20nine%20hours%20twenty-nine%20minutes%20and%2034%20members%20participated.%20The%20Rajya%20Sabha%20debated%20it%20for%20about%207%20hours%20and%2040%20members%20participated.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnother%20lie%26quot%3B%2C%20he%20said%2C%20was%20that%20the%20Bills%20were%20brought%20after%20the%20mass%20suspension%20of%20MPs.%20%26quot%3BThe%20Bill%20was%20listed%20beforehand%20by%20the%20business%20advisory%20committee.%20Maybe%20the%20Opposition%20did%20not%20want%20to%20participate.%20So%20they%20resorted%20to%20activities%20so%20that%20presiding%20officers%20are%20compelled%20to%20suspend%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Home%20Minister%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Shah%20said%20his%20ministry%20had%20sought%20suggestions%20from%20all%20MPs%2C%20Chief%20Ministers%2C%20Supreme%20Court%20and%20high%20court%20judges%20and%20bureaucrats%20on%20the%20new%20laws.%20%26quot%3BAll%20these%20suggestions%20were%20studied.%20I%20chaired%20158%20meetings%20to%20discuss%20the%20issue%20and%20we%20came%20up%20with%20a%20Bill.%20But%20the%20Parliament%20didn't%20clear%20it%20just%20like%20that.%20It%20was%20sent%20to%20the%20Standing%20Committee.%20It%20was%20against%20discussed%20for%20three%20months%20and%20members%20of%20all%20parties%20participated%20in%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Shah%20said%20his%20ministry%20had%20sought%20suggestions%20from%20all%20MPs%2C%20Chief%20Ministers%2C%20Supreme%20Court%20and%20high%20court%20judges%20and%20bureaucrats%20on%20the%20new%20laws.%20%26quot%3BAll%20these%20suggestions%20were%20studied.%20I%20chaired%20158%20meetings%20to%20discuss%20the%20issue%20and%20we%20came%20up%20with%20a%20Bill.%20But%20the%20Parliament%20didn't%20clear%20it%20just%20like%20that.%20It%20was%20sent%20to%20the%20Standing%20Committee.%20It%20was%20against%20discussed%20for%20three%20months%20and%20members%20of%20all%20parties%20participated%20in%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BApart%20from%20four-five%20political-style%20suggestions%2C%20every%20suggestion%20was%20imbibed%2C%2093%20amendments%20made%20and%20the%20Bill%20was%20cleared%20by%20the%20cabinet%20again%20and%20then%20tabled%20it%20in%20Parliament.%20To%20give%20a%20political%20colour%20to%20such%20an%20extensive%20exercise%20happening%20after%20centuries%20is%20not%20right.%20I%20appeal%20to%20friends%20in%20the%20Opposition%2C%20there%20are%20many%20issues%20for%20politics%2C%20but%20these%20laws%20are%20an%20exercise%20to%20ensure%20timely%20justice%20and%20self-respect%20for%20140%20crore%20people.%20So%20please%20cooperate%20and%20if%20anyone%20has%20anything%20to%20say%2C%20my%20office%20is%20open%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719823560000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Flog9q22g_amit-shah-_625x300_11_June_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ffocus-on-speedy-justice-says-amit-shah-as-new-criminal-laws-come-into-force-6008431%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Justice%20replaces%20punishment%20in%20the%20three%20new%20criminal%20laws%20that%20came%20into%20force%20today%2C%20Union%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20has%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ffocus-on-speedy-justice-says-amit-shah-as-new-criminal-laws-come-into-force-6008431%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%