r%20Kharge%2C%20%26quot%3BPlease%20Kharge%C2%A0%3Cem%3Eji%3C%2Fem%3E%20my%20suggestion...%20my%20suggestion%20for%20your%20consideration.%20The%20House%20is%20hearing%20you%20but%20if%20the%20House%20Leader%20wants%20to%20intervene%2C%20then%20practice%20is%20to%20allow.%20I%20leave%20to%20your%20discretion...%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kharge%2C%20however%2C%20would%20not%20back%20down%20without%20a%20fight%2C%20and%20shot%20back%2C%20%26quot%3BKindly%20allow%20me%20to%20finish%20(my%20speech)%20otherwise%20my%20flow%20will%20be%20broken%20and%20they%20(the%20BJP%20MPs)%20will%20keep%20yelling.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20is%20this%3F%20When%20we%20want%20to%20intervene%20you%20don't%20let%20us...%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20after%20Mr%20Nadda's%20green%20light.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20My%20Ears%20Heard...%26quot%3B%20Nadda's%20Counter%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20wish%20I%20could%20be%20proved%20wrong...%20but%20what%20my%20ears%20heard%20were%20an%20aspersion%20that%20you%20will%2C%20for%20the%20next%20three-and-a-half%20years%20be%20'fair'%20in%20the%20House.%20This%20means%20for%20the%20past%20one-and-a-half%20years%20you%20did%20not%20give%20opposition%20its%20due%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Nadda%20said%20after%20the%20Chair%20forced%20Mr%20Kharge%20to%20be%20silent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20a%20very%20serious%20allegation...%20it%20cannot%20be%20taken%20lightly%20as%20it%20is%20a%20sentence%20spoken%20by%20the%20LoP%20(Leader%20of%20the%20Opposition)%20and%20automatically%20means%20in%20the%20past%20you%20have%20not%20been%20fair%20to%20all.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Nadda%2C%20anger%20writ%20large%20on%20his%20face%2C%20then%20lashed%20out%20at%20opposition%20benches%20heckling%20him%20and%20shouted%20back%20'you%20please%20keep%20quiet...%20keep%20quiet...%20I%20have%20been%20given%20by%20Chairperson%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20respect%20the%20LoP...%20