20had%20just%20two%20balls%20to%20face.%20So%20I%20thought%20India's%20batting%20was%20good%2C%20but%20Virat%20Kohli%20had%20potentially%20played%20an%20innings%20that%20would've%20put%20India%20in%20a%20tight%20corner.%20And%20it%20almost%20proved%20to%20be%20that%2C%20before%20these%20guys'%20bowlers%20came%20in%20the%20end.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIndia%20were%20in%20a%20losing%20position%2C%2090%20percent%20winning%20chances%20(for%20South%20Africa).%20The%20complete%20turnaround%20actually%20saved%20Virat%20Kohli's%20innings%20because%20he%20played%20virtually%20half%20the%20innings%20with%20a%20strike-rate%20of%20128.%20My%20Player%20of%20the%20Match%20would've%20been%20a%20bowler%20because%20they%20actually%20took%20the%20game%20from%20the%20jaws%20of%20defeat%20and%20won%20it%20for%20India%2C%26quot%3B%20Manjrekar%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20Zimbabwe%20cricketer%2C%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Andy%20Flower%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F189-andy-flower-playerprofile%5C%22%3EAndy%20Flower%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20however%2C%20had%20a%20slightly%20different%20perspective.%20According%20to%20him%2C%20India%20had%20done%20enough%20with%20the%20bat%20by%20putting%20a%20total%20of%20176%20runs%20on%20the%20board.%20But%2C%20he%20did%20admit%20that%20had%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Rohit%20Sharma%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F857-rohit-sharma-playerprofile%5C%22%3ERohit%20Sharma%3C%2Fa%3E's%20men%20lost%20the%20match%2C%20Kohli%20would've%20courted%20plenty%20of%20criticism.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20India%20had%20been%20pipped%20there%2C%20there%20would've%20been%20a%20lot%20of%20criticism%20going%20Virat%20Kohli's%20way%2C%20I'd%20reckon.%20At%20the%20halfway%20mark%2C%20I%20thought%20India%20had%20enough%2C%20and%20that%20it%20was%20going%20to%20be%20a%20very%20difficult%20chase%20for%20South%20Africa%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719821820000%2