d%20me.%26quot%3B%20This%20evoked%20another%20round%20of%20laughter%20in%20the%20House.%20Former%20UPA%20spokesperson%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20was%20also%20seen%20smiling.%20The%20Congress%20president%20then%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BMr%20Chairman%20also%20misleads%20me.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EResponding%20to%20this%2C%20Mr%20Dhankhar%20quipped%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20will%20delete%20this%2C%20that%20I%20do%20it%20too.%26quot%3B%20This%20time%2C%20it%20was%20Mr%20Kharge's%20turn%20to%20laugh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMore%20banter%20was%20the%20follow.%20In%20his%20response%20to%20the%20President's%20address%2C%20Mr%20Kharge%20said%20it%20was%20just%20focused%20on%20praising%20the%20government.%20At%20his%20point%2C%20the%20Congress%20president%20started%20referring%20to%20the%20speech%20by%20BJP%20MP%20Sudhanshu%20Trivedi.%20%26quot%3BExcuse%20me%2C%20I%20sometimes%20get%20confused%20between%20Dwivedi%2C%20Trivedi%20and%20Chaturvedi.%20I%20come%20from%20the%20South%20so%20I%20am%20not%20well-aware%20of%20this%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20as%20the%20members%20banged%20the%20benches.%20Mr%20Dhankhar%20said%20with%20a%20smile%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20can%20have%20a%20half-an-hour%20discussion%20on%20this%20if%20you%20want.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20light%20banter%20was%20in%20stark%20contrast%20from%20the%20mood%20in%20the%20House%20on%20Friday%20when%20Opposition%20members%20drew%20strong%20remarks%20from%20the%20Chairman%20for%20entering%20the%20Well.%20The%20Opposition%20MPs%20were%20demanding%20a%20debate%20on%20the%20irregularities%20in%20the%20National%20Eligibility%20cum%20Entrance%20Test%20for%20medical%20admissions%20in%20colleges%20across%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Dhankhar%20had%20then%20said%20he%20was%20%26quot%3Bpained%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bshocked%26quot%3B%20that%20the%20Leader%20of%20the%20Opposition%20had%20come%20to%20the%20Well.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20response%2C%20the%20Congress%20chief%20had%20said%20he%20was%20compelled%20to%20enter%20the%20Well%20because%20the%20Chairman%20%26quot%3Bdeliberately%20ignored%20me%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20his%20mistake...%20I%20went%20inside%20(the%20Well)%20to%20draw%20his%20attention...%20I%20was%20drawing%20his%20attention.%20He%20was%20only%20looking%20at%20the%20ruling%20party.%20As%20per%20the%20rules%2C%20he%20should%20look%20at%20me%20when%20I%20draw%20his%20attention.%20But%20instead%2C%20he%20deliberately%20ignored%20me%20to%20insult%20me.%20So%20what%20option%20was%20left%3F%20To%20draw%20attention%2C%20I%20would%20have%20to%20go%20inside%20or%20shout%20very%20loudly.%20I%20will%20definitely%20say%20that%20it%20is%20Chairman%20Sahab's%20mistake.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719816300000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2Fib736ok8_kharge-dhankhar_625x300_01_July_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fjagdeep-dhankhar-mallikarjun-kharge-rajya-sabha-well-delete-this-m-kharge-veep-share-laughs-days-after-heated-exchange-6007952%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Two%20days%20after%20Rajya%20Sabha%20Chairman%20Jagdeep%20Dhankhar%20said%20he%20was%20pained%20when%20Leader%20of%20the%20Opposition%20and%20Congress%20chief%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20entered%20the%20well%20of%20the%20House%20to%20protest%2C%20the%20two%20leaders%20shared%20several%20light%20moments%20this%20morning.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fjagdeep-dhankhar-mallikarjun-kharge-rajya-sabha-well-delete-this-m-kharge-veep-share-laughs-days-after-heated-exchange-6007952%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fjagdeep-dhankhar-mallikarjun-kharge-rajya-sabha-well-delete-this-m-kharge-veep-share-laughs-days-after-heated-exchange-6007952%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fjagdeep-dhankhar-mallikarjun-kharge-rajya-sabha-well-delete-thi