n%20BJP-ruled%20states.%20But%20we%20have%20never%20heard%20a%20BJP%20leader%20say%20it's%20wrong.%20This%20can%20only%20happen%20in%20Bengal%20because%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress%20has%20a%20zero%20tolerance%20policy%20and%20we%20don't%20just%20say%20it%2C%20but%20we%20do%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20shocking%20video%20in%20which%20a%20man%20is%20seeing%20thrashing%20a%20woman%20and%20another%20man%20in%20public%20as%20a%20crowd%20watches%20has%20triggered%20massive%20outrage%20and%20scathing%20criticism%20of%20the%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20government.%20The%20BJP%20and%20the%20CPM%20have%20targeted%20the%20Trinamool%20government%20and%20drawn%20parallels%20between%20the%20state's%20law%20and%20order%20situation%20and%20a%20'kangaroo'%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Opposition%20parties%20have%20alleged%20that%20the%20main%20accused%2C%20Tajemul%2C%20has%20links%20with%20local%20Trinamool%20MLA%20Hamidur%20Rahman.%20The%20MLA%20has%20denied%20any%20connection%20with%20the%20accused.%20He%20has%20said%20it%20was%20a%20village%20matter%20and%20not%20related%20to%20the%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20woman%20in%20the%20video%2C%20it%20is%20learnt%2C%20had%20eloped%20with%20a%20man%20following%20an%20extramarital%20affair.%20The%20MLA%20described%20her%20as%20%26quot%3Bcharacterless%26quot%3B%20while%20admitting%20that%20the%20%26quot%3Bpunishment%20was%20excessive%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMain%20Opposition%20BJP%20has%20torn%20into%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress%20over%20the%20issue.%20BJP%20spokesperson%20Gaurav%20Bhatia%20told%20the%20media%20today%20that%20the%20West%20Bengal%20is%20now%20under%20%26quot%3BTaliban%20rule%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BWhether%20it%20is%20Sandeshkhali%20or%20poll%20violence%20or%20rape%20or%20murder%2C%20it%20is%20Mamata%20Banerjee's%20responsibility.%20The%20state%20home%20ministry%20is%20under%20you%20and%20law%20and%20order%20has%20been%20razed%2C%20you%20must%20resign%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%