205_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Findustry%2Fauto%2Fev-sales-drop-14-to-106-081-units-in-june-signals-challenging-road-ahead-124070100205_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Findustry%2Fauto%2Fev-sales-drop-14-to-106-081-units-in-june-signals-challenging-road-ahead-124070100205_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Macron's%20Party%20Headed%20For%20Defeat%20After%20Strong%20Showing%20By%20France's%20Far-Right%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFrance's%20far%20right%20was%20on%20Sunday%20eyeing%20a%20historic%20chance%20to%20form%20a%20government%20and%20claim%20the%20post%20of%20prime%20minister%20after%20winning%20the%20first%20round%20of%20legislative%20elections%20with%20the%20centrist%20forces%20of%20President%20Emmanuel%20Macron%20coming%20in%20only%20third.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20it%20remained%20unclear%20if%20the%20far-right%20National%20Rally%20(RN)%20party%20of%20Marine%20Le%20Pen%20would%20win%20the%20absolute%20majority%20of%20seats%20in%20the%20new%20National%20Assembly%20in%20the%20July%207%20second%20round.%20That%20is%20what%20it%20would%20need%20to%20be%20certain%20of%20taking%20power%20and%20for%20Le%20Pen's%20protege%20Jordan%20Bardella%2C%2028%2C%20to%20become%20prime%20minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMacron%20had%20stunned%20the%20nation%20and%20baffled%20even%20some%20allies%20by%20calling%20snap%20polls%20after%20the%20RN%20trounced%20his%20centrist%20forces%20in%20European%20Parliament%20elections%20this%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20that%20gamble%20risks%20backfiring%2C%20with%20Macron's%20alliance%20now%20expected%20to%20win%20a%20far%20smaller%20minority%20contingent%20in%20parliament.%20That%20would%20make%20the%20president%20a%20far%20less%20powerful%20figure%20for%20the%20remaining%20three%20years%20of%20his%20term.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProjections%20from%20prominent%20French%20polling%20firms%20gave%20the%20RN%2033.2-33.5%20percent%20of%20the%20vote%2C%20compared%20to%2028.1-28.5%20percent%20for%20the%20left-wing%20New%20Popular%20Front%20alliance%2C%20and%2021.0-22.1%20percent%20for%20Macron's%20centrist%20camp.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20polling%20agencies%20projected%20this%20would%20give%20the%20RN%20a%20majority%20of%20seats%20in%20the%20577-seat%20National%20Assembly%20after%20the%20second%20round.%20But%20it%20was%20far%20from%20clear%20the%20party%20would%20garner%20the%20289%20seats%20needed%20for%20an%20absolute%20majority.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20projections%20varied%20sharply%2C%20with%20Ipsos%20forecasting%20230-280%20seats%2C%20Ifop%20240-270%20and%20Elabe%20the%20only%20organisation%20to%20put%20it%20in%20the%20range%20of%20an%20absolute%20majority%20on%20260-310%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%2C%20Macron%20called%20for%20a%20%26quot%3Bbroad%26quot%3B%20alliance%20against%20the%20far%20right%20in%20the%20second%20round%2C%20which%20will%20see%20run-off%20votes%20where%20there%20was%20no%20outright%20winner%20in%20the%20first%20round.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20leftwing%20alliance%20and%20the%20president's%20camp%20will%20be%20hoping%20that%20tactical%20voting%20to%20prevent%20RN%20candidates%20winning%20seats%20will%20leave%20it%20short%20of%20the%20absolute%20majority.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrench%20Prime%20Minister%20Gabriel%20Attal%2C%20who%20is%20likely%20to%20be%20forced%20to%20resign%20after%20the%20second%20round%2C%20warned%20the%20far%20right%20was%20now%20at%20the%20%26quot%3Bgates%20of%20power%26quot%3B.%20The%20RN%20should%20not%20get%20a%20%26quot%3Bsingle%20vote%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20second%20round%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20seven%20days%20to%20spare%20France%20from%20catastrophe%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Raphael%20Glucksmann%2C%20a%20key%20figure%20in%20the%20left-wing%20alliance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Prime%20minister%20of%20all%20French'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20French%20facing%20their%20most%20polarising%20choices%20in%20recent%20history%2C%20turnout%20soared%20to%2065%20percent%2C%20way%20above%20the%20turnout%20in%202022%20polls%20of%20just%2047.5%20percent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMacron%20said%20the%20high%20turnout%20in%20the%20first%20round%20spoke%20of%20%26quot%3Bthe%20importance%20of%20this%20vote%20for%20all%20our%20compatriots%20and%20the%20desire%20to%20clarify%20the%20political%20situation%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20arrival%20of%20anti-immigration%20and%20eurosceptic%20RN%20in%20government%20would%20be%20a%20turning%20point%20in%20French%20modern%20history%20and%20be%20the%20first%20time%20a%20far-right%20force%20has%20taken%20power%20in%20the%20country%20since%20World%20War%20II%20when%20it%20was%20occupied%20by%20Nazi%20Germany.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNothing%20is%20won%20and%20the%20second%20round%20is%20decisive%2C%26quot%3B%20Le%20Pen%2C%20who%20has%20long%20worked%20to%20distance%20the%20party%20from%20its%20extremist%20origins%2C%20told%20supporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20need%20an%20absolute%20majority%20so%20that%20Jordan%20Bardella%20is%20in%20eight%20days%20named%20prime%20minister%20by%20Emmanuel%20Macron.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBardella%20said%20he%20wanted%20to%20be%20the%20%26quot%3Bprime%20minister%20of%20all%20French%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20would%20create%20a%20tense%20period%20of%20%26quot%3Bcohabitation%26quot%3B%20with%20Macron%2C%20who%20has%20vowed%20to%20serve%20out%20his%20term%20until%202027.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBardella%20has%20said%20he%20will%20only%20form%20a%20government%20if%20the%20RN%20wins%20an%20absolute%20majority%20in%20the%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Heavy%20defeat'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20alternative%20is%20months%20of%20political%20paralysis%20and%20negotiations%20to%20find%20a%20solution%20for%20a%20sustainable%20government%20that%20can%20survive%20no-confidence%20votes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHard-left%20leader%20Jean-Luc%20Melenchon%20said%20Macron's%20centrist%20alliance%20had%20suffered%20a%20%26quot%3Bheavy%20and%20undisputable%26quot%3B%20defeat%20in%20the%20snap%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERisk%20analysis%20firm%20Eurasia%20Group%20said%20the%20RN%20now%20looked%20%26quot%3Blikely%26quot%3B%20to%20fall%20short%20of%20an%20absolute%20majority.%20France%20was%20facing%20%26quot%3Bat%20least%2012%20months%20with%20a%20rancorously%20blocked%20National%20Assembly%20and%20--%20at%20best%20--%20a%20technocratic%20government%20of%20'national%20unity'%20with%20limited%20capacity%20to%20govern%26quot%3B%2C%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMacron's%20decision%20to%20call%20the%20snap%20vote%20sparked%20uncertainty%20in%20Europe's%20second-biggest%20economy.%20The%20Paris%20stock%20exchange%20suffered%20its%20biggest%20monthly%20decline%20in%20two%20years%20in%20June%2C%20dropping%20by%206.4%20percent%2C%20according%20to%20figures%20released%20on%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20turmoil%20also%20risks%20undermining%20Macron's%20stature%20as%20an%20international%20leader%20taking%20a%20prime%20role%20in%20helping%20Ukraine%20fight%20the%20Russian%20invasion.%20In%20the%20immediate%20aftermath%20of%20the%20second%20round%20he%20is%20due%20to%20attend%20the%20NATO%20summit%20in%20Washington.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrench%20daily%20Liberation%20urged%20voters%20to%20unite%20to%20halt%20the%20march%20of%20the%20far-right.%20%26quot%3BAfter%20the%20shock%2C%20form%20a%20block%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20newspaper%20said%20on%20its%20Monday%20front%20page.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719809580000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2F4bm8n8so_macron-_625x300_01_July_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-