2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20changes%20coming%20into%20force%20today%20will%20help%20restore%20integrity%20to%20our%20international%20education%20system%2C%20and%20create%20a%20migration%20system%20which%20is%20fairer%2C%20smaller%20and%20better%20able%20to%20deliver%20for%20Australia%2C%26quot%3B%20Home%20Affairs%20Minister%20Clare%20O'Neil%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOfficial%20data%20released%20in%20March%20showed%20net%20immigration%20rose%2060%25%20to%20a%20record%20548%2C800%20people%20in%20the%20year%20to%20Sept.%2030%2C%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20rise%20in%20fees%20makes%20applying%20for%20a%20student%20visa%20for%20Australia%20far%20more%20expensive%20than%20in%20competing%20countries%20like%20the%20U.S.%20and%20Canada%2C%20where%20they%20cost%20about%20%24185%20and%20C%24150%20(%24110)%20respectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20said%20it%20was%20also%20closing%20loopholes%20in%20visa%20rules%20that%20allowed%20foreign%20students%20to%20continuously%20extend%20their%20stay%20in%20Australia%2C%20after%20the%20number%20of%20students%20on%20a%20second%20or%20subsequent%20student%20visa%20spiked%20by%20over%2030%25%20to%20more%20than%20150%2C000%20in%202022-23.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20latest%20move%20follows%20a%20raft%20of%20actions%20since%20late%20last%20year%20to%20tighten%20the%20student%20visa%20rules%20as%20the%20lifting%20of%20COVID-19%20curbs%20in%202022%20boosted%20annual%20migration%20to%20record%20levels.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEnglish%20language%20requirements%20were%20tightened%20in%20March%2C%20while%20the%20amount%20of%20savings%20international%20students%20need%20to%20get%20a%20visa%20was%20raised%20in%20May%20to%20A%2429%2C710%20(%2419%2C823)%20from%20A%2424%2C505%2C%20the%20second%20increase%20in%20about%20seven%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUniversities%20Australia%20CEO%20Luke%20Sheehy%20said%20the%20government's%20continued%20policy%20pressure%20on%20the%20sector%20would%20put%20the%20country's%20position%20of%20strength%20at%20risk.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20not%20good%20for%20our%20economy%20or%20our%20universities%2C%20both%20of%20which%20rely%20heavily%20on%20international%20student%20fees%2C%26quot%3B%20Sheehy%20said%20in%20an%20emailed%20response.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInternational%20education%20is%20one%20of%20Australia's%20largest%20export%20industries%20and%20was%20worth%20A%2436.4%20billion%20to%20the%20economy%20in%20the%202022-2023%20financial%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719801840000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2F8orcoa9_australia_625x300_01_July_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Faustralia-doubles-foreign-student-visa-fee-to-tackle-migration-6006700%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Australia%20said%20on%20Monday%20it%20had%20more%20than%20doubled%20the%20visa%20fee%20for%20international%20students%2C%20the%20latest%20move%20by%20the%20government%20to%20rein%20in%20record%20migration%20that%20has%20intensified%20pressure%20on%20an%20already%20tight%20housing%20market.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Faustralia-doubles-foreign-student-visa-fee-to-tackle-migration-6006700%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Faustralia-doubles-foreign-student-visa-fee-to-tackle-migration-6006700%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Faustralia-doubles-foreign-student-visa-fee-to-tackle-migration-6006700%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Australia%20foreign%20student%20visa%20policy%20changes%3A%20Fees%20doubled%2C%20extension%20gets%20difficult%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22