as%20baffled%20by%20this%20blind-sided%20hate.%20He%20was%20even%20more%20amused%20when%20the%20rhetoric%20would%20witness%20a%20flip%20during%20Pride%20Month.%20And%20this%20made%20him%20think%20along%20the%20lines%20of%20starting%20an%20initiative%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F334508%2Finspiring-story-of-sex-worker-turned-artist-aravani-art-project-for-transgenders%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehelp%20trans%20persons%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%E2%80%9CI%20wanted%20to%20do%20something%20that%20would%20make%20their%20%5Btrans%20persons%E2%80%99%5D%20struggles%20an%20ongoing%20subject%20of%20conversation%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Ishnoor%20hadn%E2%80%99t%20quite%20put%20a%20finger%20on%20a%20formal%20model%2C%20it%20was%20a%20chance%20meeting%20with%20Dhananjay%20that%20gave%20his%20vision%20structure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20conversation%20ensued%2C%20the%20latter%20began%20to%20relay%20the%20struggle%20she%20had%20to%20endure%20to%20get%20her%20food%20truck%20up%20and%20running.%20%E2%80%9CDhananjay%20recounted%20how%20the%20local%20administrations%20hadn%E2%80%99t%20been%20supportive%20and%20getting%20permissions%20was%20a%20hassle.%20She%20was%20disappointed%20at%20how%20the%20truck%20was%20simply%20wasting%20away%20and%20not%20helping%20her%20generate%20income%20%E2%80%94%20which%20was%20the%20intention%20with%20which%20it%20was%20donated%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ishnoor%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ciframe%20referrerpolicy%3D%5C%22strict-origin-when-cross-origin%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2Fz3LszbYKybU%3Fsi%3D0R-uN-RJRZY1_hft%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGathering%20a%20couple%20of%20his%20friends%2C%20Ishnoor%20began%20ideating%20on%20the%20best%20way%20to%20navigate%20this%20sticky%20situation.%20He%20approached%20Hitesh%20Bharadwaj%2C%20PA%20to%20the%20District%20Commissioner%20of%20Chandigarh%2C%20who%20confirmed%20guiding%20the%20students%20in%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20students%2C%20with%20Bharadwaj%E2%80%99s%20help%2C%20arrived%20at%20the%20solution%20that%20if%20setting%20up%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F311520%2Flearn-how-to-start-food-truck-business-better-mentor-south-indian-food-jyoti-satya%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20food%20truck%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Chandigarh%20was%20proving%20to%20be%20a%20hassle%20because%20of%20permissions%2C%20they%20could%20set%20their%20sights%20on%20Zirakpur%2C%20a%2025-minute%20drive%20from%20Chandigarh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20spoke%20to%20the%20people%20from%20the%20market%20association%20at%20VIP%20Road%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ishnoor%20notes.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20they%20demanded%20rent%20for%20Dhananjay%20to%20set%20up%20the%20food%20truck%20business%2C%20we%20chipped%20in%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWere%20there%20hurdles%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COf%20course%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20responds.%20%E2%80%9CVIP%20Road%20is%20home%20to%20many%20food%20trucks%2C%20and%20initially%2C%20there%20was%20a%20lot%20of%20backlash%20about%20having%20Dhananjay%E2%80%99s%20truck%20parked%20there%20too.%20The%20other%20food%20truck%20owners%20put%20on%20a%20fuss%20that%20their%20trucks%20would%20be%20concealed%20by%20Dhanajay%E2%80%99s.%20Eventually%2C%20we%20managed%20to%20find%20a%20spot%20where%20Dhananjay%20could%20operate%20without%20being%20in%20the%20way%20of%20the%20other%20food%20trucks.%20Everyone%20was%20happy.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECurrently%2C%20the%20truck%20is%20being%20helmed%20by%20Dhanajay%20along%20with%20Rudrapratap%20Singh%20(he%2Fhim).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201170px)%20100vw%2C%201170px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.the