ns%20persons%20revive%20their%20businesses%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Ftrans-persons-welfare-1719563005.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Ftrans-persons-welfare-1719563005-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Ftrans-persons-welfare-1719563005-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Ftrans-persons-welfare-1719563005-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Ftrans-persons-welfare-1719563005-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-354776%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EIshnoor%20Singh%20started%20project%20SoulSpectrum%20in%20an%20attempt%20to%20help%20trans%20persons%20revive%20their%20businesses%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Ishnoor%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20help%20includes%20providing%20the%20respective%20trans%20individual%20with%20trade%20credit%2C%20access%20to%20merchants%20from%20whom%20they%20can%20procure%20the%20supplies%20they%20need%2C%20and%20help%20with%20finances.%20More%20often%20than%20not%20these%20trans%20persons%E2%80%99%20struggles%20at%20%E2%80%9Cfitting%20in%E2%80%9D%20are%20unintelligible%20to%20most%20people%2C%20Ishnoor%20points%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CConversations%20with%20them%20have%20led%20me%20to%20realise%20that%20many%20of%20them%20have%20been%20marginalised%20for%20so%20long%20that%20they%20simply%20do%20not%20want%20to%20venture%20into%20corporate%20work.%20So%2C%20the%20only%20other%20route%20would%20be%20to%20run%20a%20business%20by%20themselves.%20And%20this%20is%20what%20I%20am%20helping%20with%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20cites%20trans%20woman%20Mona%20(she%2Fher)%20as%20one%20example%20of%20the%20first%20tea%20stall%20businesses%20they%20he