e%20birth%20to%20the%20entrepreneur%20inside%20the%20researcher.%20She%20decided%20to%20create%20an%20impact%20using%20her%20patented%20antimicrobial%20active%20copper%20technology.%C2%A0This%20was%20created%20along%20with%20her%20PhD%20supervisor%20Professor%20Mangala%20Joshi%20who%20is%20also%20the%20co-founder%20of%20Nanosafe.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20how%20to%20go%20about%20it%3F%20The%20answer%20to%20this%20question%20presented%20itself%20in%20the%20form%20of%20COVID-19.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20world%20was%20looking%20to%20make%20masks%20and%20there%20was%20a%20massive%20shortage%20in%20the%20beginning.%20The%20textile%20engineer%20used%20her%20patented%20technology%20and%20made%20%E2%80%98NSafe%20masks%E2%80%99%20which%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20a%20gamechanger.%20The%20fabric-based%20antimicrobial%20face%20mask%20was%20made%20in%20India%2C%20reducing%20the%20need%20for%20imports.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20960px)%20100vw%2C%20960px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-06-26-at-16.42.54-1719410205.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Dr%20Anasuya%20Roy%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-06-26-at-16.42.54-1719410205.jpeg%20960w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-06-26-at-16.42.54-1719410205-225x300.jpeg%20225w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-06-26-at-16.42.54-1719410205-500x667.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-06-26-at-16.42.54-1719410205-768x1024.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-06-26-at-16.42.54-1719410205-640x853.jpeg%20640w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.t