child.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Col%20start%3D%5C%227%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ERespect%20a%20child%3F%20Shouldn%E2%80%99t%20the%20child%20respect%20the%20adult%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20It%20is%20a%20huge%20mindset%20alteration%20in%20our%20adult-centric%20societies%20to%20acknowledge%20that%20respect%20is%20a%20two-way%20street.%20Parents%20observe%20that%20when%20they%20respect%20their%20children%2C%20listen%20to%20their%20opinions%20and%20work%20collaboratively%20with%20them%2C%20they%20automatically%20get%20more%20cooperation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EDemocracy%20isn%E2%80%99t%20just%20for%20the%20nation%3B%20it%20works%20in%20families%20too.%20Giving%20children%20choices%2C%20trusting%20and%20respecting%20them%20builds%20responsible%20people%20and%20citizens%20down%20the%20line.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Col%20start%3D%5C%228%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%9CI%20never%20knew%20that%20one%20of%20the%20most%20important%20jobs%20of%20a%20parent%20is%20to%20make%20sure%20my%20child%20feels%20loved%20and%20secure.%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EIn%20this%20fast-paced%20world%2C%20parents%20are%20so%20busy%20making%20sure%20that%20their%20child%20goes%20to%20the%20right%20school%2C%20eats%20the%20right%20food%2C%20and%20goes%20to%20the%20right%20activities%20that%20the%20fundamental%20needs%20of%20the%20child%20are%20lost.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EFeeling%20loved%2C%20valued%20and%20safe%20are%20the%20most%20fundamental%20needs%20of%20the%20growing%20child%20according%20to%20the%20latest%20information%20from%20neuroscience.%20Without%20these%20basics%2C%20learning%20cannot%20take%20place.%20The%20question%2C%20%E2%80%9CDoes%20your%20child%20feel%20loved%3F%E2%80%9D%20is%20a%20powerful%20wake-up%20call%20for%20parents.%20Learning%20how%20to%20express%20love%20often%20has%20to%20be%20taught%20as%20it%20may%20not%20come%20naturally%20for%20everyone%2C%20or%20they%20may%20have%20nev