3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EWhen%20parents%20become%20more%20empathetic%2C%20patient%2C%20and%20understanding%2C%20they%20invariably%20see%20a%20positive%20transformation%20in%20their%20child%E2%80%99s%20behaviour.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EFor%20over%20two%20decades%2C%20hearing%20these%20observations%20from%20parents%20has%20served%20as%20a%20testament%20to%20the%20transformative%20power%20of%20empowering%20them%20with%20knowledge%20and%20skills%20to%20raise%20children%20with%20kindness%20and%20connection.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIt%20also%20highlights%20the%20desire%20that%20parents%20have%20for%20information%20and%20support.%20Science%20tells%20us%20that%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fbipartisanpolicy.org%2Fdownload%2F%3Ffile%3D%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F05%2FC.-1-The-Science-of-Early-Childhood.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E90%25%20of%20brain%20development%20takes%20place%20in%20the%20first%206%20years%20of%20life%3C%2Fa%3E.%20If%20every%20parent%20received%20information%20on%20how%20to%20best%20support%20their%20children%2C%20parents%20would%20be%20changemakers.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2F2_11zon-1719403604.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Lessons%20from%20parenting%20workshops%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2F2_11zon-1719403604.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2F2_11zon-1719403604-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2F2_11zon-1719403604-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2F2_11zon-1719403604-768x402.jpg%20